author: devin
msg: Some further minor refactorings of the OdfPackage / OdfImage classes:
1) The URI interpretation that have been previously copied from OdfImage to OdfPackage has been replaced in OdfImage by a call of the new OdfPackage functionality (erased code duplicaton).
2) Every type of insert() method comes now with and without mediatype (consitency).
3) OdfPackage parameters have been renamed to be more evident (filePath -> packagePath or odfPath) and JavaDoc enhancements
